@startuml 业务架构图
!theme plain
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam linetype ortho

title Node.js 业务架构图 (TOGAF Business Architecture)

package "业务能力层" {
  [JavaScript运行时服务] as RuntimeService
  [包管理生态系统] as PackageEcosystem
  [开发者社区支持] as CommunitySupport
  [跨平台支持能力] as CrossPlatform
}

package "业务流程层" {
  [应用开发流程] as DevProcess
  [包发布流程] as PublishProcess
  [问题处理流程] as IssueProcess
  [版本发布流程] as ReleaseProcess
}

package "业务角色层" {
  [开发者] as Developers
  [维护者] as Maintainers
  [TSC技术委员会] as TSC
  [协作者] as Collaborators
  [问题分类员] as Triagers
  [发布团队] as ReleaseTeam
}

package "业务价值层" {
  [跨平台JavaScript执行] as CrossPlatformExec
  [生态系统支持] as EcosystemSupport
  [长期维护保障] as LongTermSupport
  [开放治理模式] as OpenGovernance
}

' 业务能力关系
RuntimeService --> DevProcess
PackageEcosystem --> PublishProcess
CommunitySupport --> IssueProcess
CrossPlatform --> ReleaseProcess

' 业务流程关系
DevProcess --> Developers
PublishProcess --> Maintainers
IssueProcess --> Triagers
ReleaseProcess --> ReleaseTeam

' 业务角色关系
Developers --> CrossPlatformExec
Maintainers --> EcosystemSupport
TSC --> LongTermSupport
Collaborators --> OpenGovernance
Triagers --> IssueProcess
ReleaseTeam --> ReleaseProcess

' 业务价值关系
CrossPlatformExec --> RuntimeService
EcosystemSupport --> PackageEcosystem
LongTermSupport --> CommunitySupport
OpenGovernance --> TSC

note right of RuntimeService
  **核心业务能力**
  - 提供JavaScript运行时环境
  - 支持异步I/O模型
  - 事件驱动架构
end note

note right of TSC
  **治理结构**
  - 技术决策委员会
  - 架构指导
  - 战略方向
end note

note right of LongTermSupport
  **LTS支持**
  - 每两年发布LTS版本
  - 18个月维护期
  - 安全更新保障
end note

@enduml

